My few modifications to the standard android AlarmClock.
Changed under the APACHE 2.0 license.

Extra Features:
  * Night clock mode
  * Ringtones from mp3
  * Disable during calls
  * Name alarms
  * Extra alarm settings:
      * vibrate only
      * alarm volume envelope   (start_volume increases to max_volume over envelope_duration)
      * alarm delay             (ms pause between ringtone plays)
      * alarm duration          (number of seconds to ring alarm for)
      * snooze duration         (number of minutes to snooze when pressed)
  * ?Accelerometer snooze?
